listing_company_name: LJ Hooker - West Lakes | Henley Beach
description:
Prime opportunity for you to secure the very best lake side living with a low maintenance lifestyle on offer.

Make this your next move and enjoy the-all perks of Delfin Island at hand.

Features You Will Love:
- Beaming Open-Plan Living, Dining & Kitchen Area
- Spacious Lounge With Split System Reverse Cycle Air Conditioning
- Generous Sized Kitchen Adjacent Dining Area
- Bedrooms 1 & 2 With Ceiling Fans, Built-In-Robes And Split System Reverse Cycle Air Conditioning
- Bedroom 3 With Split System Reverse Cycle Air Conditioning
- Family Sized Bathroom, Fully Tiled With Separate W/C
- Spacious Low Maintenance Yard, Securely Enclosed With Tool Shed
- Lock-Up Garage With Automatic Roller Door And Drive Through Access For Additional Two Cars
- Under Cover Pergola Entertainment Area
- Solar Panels*


Live in the highly sought-after neighbourhood of West Lakes, right up in the premium Delfin Island locale where pristine water views are the ultimate lifestyle. Enjoy picturesque morning strolls around the area, lazy afternoon brunches in the local cafes and eateries, easy access to transportation links with bus stops just by the corner and Westfield is just a few minutes' drive away to satisfy your retail cravings. Take a casual stroll to the local duck pound and enjoy the lifestyle at hand.


For more information, please contact Rosemary Auricchio on 0418 656 386
